{"tid":176711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"柏林博物館估值3500萬金幣展品失竊","createTime":"2017-03-28T10:57:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T03:08:38.000Z","uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7dbf3068dfd13e8cf2ab441a127756f8d3181aa","tid":176711,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T10:57:39.000Z","msg":"德國柏林一間博物館有一枚24K楓葉金幣展品失竊，這枚金幣重達二百二十一磅，面值一百萬美元（約七百八十萬港元），但以其重量推算，估值四百五十萬美元（近三千五百萬港元）。 <br />\n<br />\n被偷走的金幣厚一點一八吋，直徑達二十點九吋，一面鑄有英女皇伊利沙伯二世的頭像，另一面則是代表加拿大的楓葉。<br />\n<br />\n收藏這枚金幣的博德博物館指，金幣因為其千分之九百九十九點九九純度，而獲列入健力士紀錄大全。<br />\n<br />\n金幣自2010年起在博物館展出，警方相信賊人在當地星期一凌晨約三時半，利用一把長梯子爬窗闖入博物館，從防彈玻璃箱中偷走金幣。警方事後在附近的鐵路軌道旁發現一把梯，正調查賊人和金幣的下落。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k2cVb13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk2cVb13.jpg&h=d9a3a5a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7309b2bf09f33cb84e7ca535beee77b6af193665","tid":176711,"uid":70505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T10:58:48.000Z","msg":"熔左佢，神不知鬼不覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8f1b5583240063b84ce8c7d884834df89a7fee","tid":176711,"uid":89955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T10:59:06.000Z","msg":"個小小錢都要偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b79ced056b50166263fbffe9e78c49c476deda0c","tid":176711,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T10:59:56.000Z","msg":"好似某套電視劇內容"},{"pid":"443c32a17f6208a7ef9e7b058dc7a4570f39c659","tid":176711,"uid":35135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:52:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>熔左佢，神不知鬼不覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b6c6d2931c9385a209017c6726ef52bb92722a","tid":176711,"uid":81183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-